reviewText: Why don't they come out with the other episodes on dvd?
Coach has brought us many entertaining and laugh-filled nights. Wish they produced more seasons on DVD.
Love it. Now waiting to see when I can buy seasons 5,6,7,8,9.
I had two disc 2 in season one.
I always loved Coach.  The only problem I have, is that there are only 4 seasons.  Hopefully, one day there will be more.
This show was and is awesome! I just wish they would release seasons 5-9 to make my set complete.
I'm so happy they finally released more seasons of Coach. Loved this show "back then" and love it now.
Simply one of the best shows ever.  Hard to find these DVDs anywhere really and am glad I could now that the show is no longer on Netflix.  I know I'll be glad to have these around for years to come.
I am hoping more seasons will be available.
Coach is a funny series. Now I need to get seasons 5 thru 9.
Perfect gift for anyone who loves Coach! You will enjoy hours of laughs!
